AMP Saver Account

This product includes

  • A competitive savings rate
  • Easy online access to your money
  • The requirement to deposit at least $250 each month to receive the bonus interest rate
  • The ability to link your savings account to an everyday transaction account

This product doesn’t include

  • The bonus interest rate if you deposit less than $250 each month
  • A cheque book, Bank@Post or digital wallet facilities
  • No restriction on pay anyone amounts

A target market determination for this product is available at www.amp.com.au/bank/tmd
